These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, daffodil, lily, amaryllis
4 different games are played: go, poker, domino, canasta
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, house, r&b, trance
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, frog, rabbit
1. the person playing poker is the person who growssunflower##1
2. the fan of trance is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the fan of r&b is the person playing go##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person playing poker##1
5. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
6. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of house##1
7. the person playing poker is the owner of the cat##1
8. the fan of house is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
9. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Flower         | sunflower  | amaryllis  | daffodil | lily |
| Game           | poker | go | canasta  | domino  |
| Music-Genre   | trance       | r&b      | country | house      |
| Pet           | cat          | fish     | frog    | rabbit     |

