.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, sprite, tea
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, kiwi, orange, papaya
4 different games are played: canasta, go, snooker, backgammon
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, camping, reading, woodworking
1. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
2. the person playing backgammon is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person eating orange is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
5. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the person playing snooker##1
7. the person playing go is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
9. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | cola       | iced-tea | tea        |
| Food          | papaya     | kiwi       | orange   | broccoli   |
| Game   | snooker      | go       | backgammon     | canasta    |
| Hobby         | reading | woodworking | collecting | camping |

