.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, motorbike, roller, scooter
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, ivory, blue, turquise
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, lizard, mouse, pony
 1. the person drinking tea is the owner of the pony##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
 3. the person who likes blue is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 6. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
 7. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | 7up       | tea        | mirinda        |
| Transport           | motorbike   | roller | van   | scooter |
| Color   | pink     | ivory    | turquise | blue        |
| Pet           | mouse         | hedgehog  | pony       | lizard         |

