.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, engineer, firefighter, scientist
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, red, blood-red, azure
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, sports, disaster, action
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, guinea-pig, horse
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the bartender##1
2. the firefighter is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the person who likes white is on the far right##1
4. the scientist is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
5. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes red##1
6. the person who likes azure is on the right of the engineer##1
7. the scientist is on the right of the bartender##1
8. the person watching mystery movies is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Job           | engineer   | bartender  | scientist | firefighter |
| Color   | blood-red | azure       | red       | white     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster       | action    | sports     | mystery  |
| Pet           | ferret     | guinea-pig | horse     | cat         |

