.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, social-worker, teacher, videographer
House: townhouse, cape-cod, colonial, gothic-revival
There are 4 different nationalities: french, indian, thai, turkish
City: rome, marseilles, new-york, nizza
1. the colonial house is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the analyst##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1
4. the indian is on the left of the french##1
5. the turkish is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
6. the person traveling to nizza is the thai##1
7. the french is on the left of the townhouse house##1
8. the social-worker is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
9. the townhouse house is on the right of the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Job           | analyst  | teacher    | social-worker | videographer |
| House   | colonial      | cape-cod    | townhouse         | gothic-revival    |
| Nationality   | indian   | french     | thai          | turkish      |
| City         | marseilles | rome | nizza      | new-york      |

