.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, russian, colombian, mexican
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, game, havana, siglo
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, mystery, scientific, thriller
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, horse, mouse
 1. the colombian is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 2. the malaysian is the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the tiparillo-smoker is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the owner of the horse is the malaysian##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the siglo-smoker##1
 6. the colombian is on the left of the russian##1
 7. the havana-smoker is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the havana-smoker is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the fish is on the left of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Nationality          | malaysian  | mexican | colombian     | russian |
| Cigar           | havana  | siglo      | tiparillo | game    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | scientific  | fantasy    | thriller  |
| Pet           | horse   | mouse       | fish       | frog      |

