.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, american, indian, canadian
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, cooking, sudoku, woodworking
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hedgehog, pony
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, trance, disco, dubstep
 1. the owner of the bird is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 2. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the american##1
 3. the indian is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 7. the owner of the bird is the fan of disco##1
 8. the italian is on the far left##1
 9. the italian is on the left of the american##1
10. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Nationality    | italian | american     | indian    | canadian |
| Hobby       | baking | sudoku    | woodworking | cooking |
| Pet         | frog   | hedgehog  | pony        | bird    |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | trance | techno    | disco |

