.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-9::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, chess, scrabble, go
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, classical, disco, metal
4 different pets are kept: frog, hedgehog, mouse, pony
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, mirinda, soy-milk
1. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the fan of classical is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is the person playing go##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the frog##1
8. the fan of disco is on the far left##1
9. the fan of metal is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Game         | chess | go | scrabble | monopoly     |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | metal       | blues       | classical  |
| Pet           | pony    | hedgehog    | mouse       | frog       |
| Beverage     | cola     | soy-milk        | fanta   | mirinda |

