6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the teacher##1
7. the malaysian is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the fan of metal##1
9. the argentine is on the right of the journalist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
| Music-Genre      | salsa     | metal           | techno    | rock    |
| Hobby         | traveling  | rock-climbing | drawing  | video-games |
