 4. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
 5. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
10. the person eating garlic is the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3       |     4     |
